#bg {
  width: 500px;
  height: 500px;   #1            #2       #3
  background: url('yaakov.png') no-repeat top center; #1 image url , #2 tells how many times to repeat , #3 position of image
  background-color: blue; # image hass higher presedance than bg colour
}
 OR 
#bg {
  width: 500px;
  height: 500px;   
  background-color: blue;
  background-image: url('yaakov.png');
  background-repeat:no-repeat;
  background-postion : top center;
} 
 #if use background: url('yaakov.png') no-repeat top center; then mention color seprately again as bg image will over rides bg color

